Making an ISO (Steps)
1. Install Iso Burner CD/DVD
2. Install ISO recorder CD/DVD
3. USE RUFUS by AIKO for USB ISO's copy

REVIEW > ISO'S are block copy Images
	   > ISO's can be used as backup or installation media
